  {{After the fall of Atlas and Ironwood's fall, when Team RWBY felt lost and isolated from everyone they knew. The Grimm king and his Grimm Knights came and captured Team RWBY. And forced them to become the Grimm Girls and serve him.}}

{{All four girls now have pale white skin, red eyes, and horns.}}

{{They can no longer use aura and their semblances because of being Grimm-Human hybrids. But in its place are unique powers and superhuman abilities.}}

{{Ruby Rose is now given the title of Grimm Maiden. Her once silver eyes now turn gold which gives her enhanced perception that allows her to see fast-moving objects and, some amount of predictive capabilities: she can anticipate an opponent's next move based on the slightest muscle tension in their body and act accordingly to dodge or intercept.}}

{{Ruby wields a living weapon. Her living weapon is a scythe named Blitz. Blitz can transform into a black wolf.}}

{{Ruby the fastest among the four. Being able to move at mach three.}}

{{Weiss Schnee is now given the title of Winter Valkyrie. She now has abilities similar to a vampire. She can also grow wings on her back. Her weapon is now a powerful sentient sword named Vladimir.}}

{{Vladimir is the sentient sword that Weiss wields. Vladimir can create ice and inflict frostbite to anyone he cuts. He speaks in a British accent and is sarcastic, often just to annoy Weiss.}}

{{Blake Belladonna is given the title of Night Hunter. Her arms have been replaced with tentacles that has sharp claws that she can use as whips. She wears a mask to hide her mouth with jagged teeth. Her four other senses had been heightened, her tongue has venom that paralyzes her opponents.}}

{{Yang Xiao Long is given the monicker of Fire Fury. Her right arm is no longer mechanical. It has been replaced with a grimm arm. She can spew lava from her mouth. She now wields as double barrel shotgun named Houlong. She is the physically strongest among the four.}}

{{Yang's right forearm is slightly larger than her left.}}

{{They all hate the Grimm King for turning them into his minions.}}

{{They just follow his orders because the Grimm King is stronger them the four of them combined.}}

{{They are lower in rank compared to the Grimm King's ten Grimm Knights.}}

{{They however serves as the bodyguards of the Grimm King.}}
